    <summaries>
      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p> Calls for the recognition of all families that have lost loved ones in uniform.</p> <p> Urges the President to encourage military bases around the country to: (1) organize and host events to recognize and commemorate the sacrifices of members of the Armed Forces, and (2) encourage families within the local area that have lost loved ones in combat to attend. <BR> </p>]]></text>
